&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify &amp;amp; execute upsell and cross-sell opportunities across a broad portfolio to enhance client value and devise strategies to capitalize on them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide prompt and effective support to address client needs and inquiries.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct regular performance reviews and gather client feedback.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to resolve client issues and requests promptly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stay abreast of industry trends and market developments to anticipate client needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally to execute strategies to support clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
