&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Demonstrate resourcefulness and flexibility in navigating changing environments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain a thorough understanding of company products and services to provide accurate information and support to clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Look For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
